Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinement for compound 1

| Empirical formula | C6H4ClCu2NO2 |
|-------------------|-------------|
| Formula weight    | 284.63      |
| Temperature (K)   | 293(2)      |
| Wavelength (Å)    | 0.71073     |
| Crystal system    | orthorhombic|
| Space group       | P212121     |
| a (Å)             | 19.065(4)   |
| b (Å)             | 3.7262(7)   |
| c (Å)             | 10.572(2)   |
| Volume (Å³)       | 751.0(3)    |
| Z                 | 4           |
| Goodness-of-fit on F² | 1.119   |
| Final R indices [I >2σ(I)] | R1=0.0560, wR2=0.1175 |
| Indices (all data)| R1=0.0763, wR2=0.1245 |

a. R1 = ∑ ∥Fo|-|Fc∥ / ∑ |Fo|
b. wR2 = { ∑ [w(Fo²-Fc²)] / ∑ [w(Fo²)] }¹/²

[^a]: Goodness-of-fit on F²
[^b]: Final R indices [I >2σ(I)]
